      },
      "date": "2025-02-07 14:39:36.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Patch Set 1:\n> \n> Peter told me this was discussed at LWG and this is the action and Tim was going to submit the change, but since it did not happen today, I asked Alex to do it.\n\nI originally thought we upgraded from 2.2.5 -> 2.2.6. I was skeptical openZFS would change the defaults in such a small release. But it was really 2.1.15 -> 2.2.6. And James found the commit  the changed the default 56fa4aa96eb3875f254e93eaef646ea20ba187f9. So https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/57990 seemed more reasonable in that context.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
