        },
        "subject": "LU-18704 build: use ZFS 2.1.15",
        "message": "LU-18704 build: use ZFS 2.1.15\n\nrevert ZFS version to 2.1.15 as 2.2.6 enables compression by default\nand this breaks many tests (like sanity/66 expecting exact blocks).\n\nFixes: 56bb6438aa (\"LU-18387 kernel: RHEL 9.5 server support\")\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nTest-Parameters: fstype=zfs testlist=sanity\nTest-Parameters: fstype=zfs testlist=sanity-quota\nTest-Parameters: fstype=zfs testlist=ost-pools\nSigned-off-by: Alex Zhuravlev <bzzz@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I2d295df1dd724961df05596bcd38270f33208b75\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
